features: SPACE SAVING -Clear precious—or nonexistent—drawer space without forgoing an organized kitchen. The utensil caddy is large enough to enable you to keep all the kitchen utensils you own on your countertop. Compact and dainty, it takes up little space and is easy to store should you wish to do so.
EASY ACCESS -The utensil holder rotates easily and smoothly with just the tip of a finger. Conveniently access any and all utensils while cooking, serving, or grilling. Utensils are not included.

VERSATILE ORGANIZATION- A sturdy divider sections the caddy, enabling you to keep different utensils in different compartments. Divider is removable to fit more and for easy cleaning. Store your spatulas, ladles, tongs, peelers, knives, whisks, can openers, and turners in the manner that suits you best.
STEADY GRIP -The holder is set on a sturdy plastic base with a steady grip. Will sit firmly on countertop even as you rotate the caddy. Won’t slip, slide, or wobble.

MATT STAINLESS STEEL -Of matt stainless, the caddy has an attractively modern appearance that matches your kitchen decor. Unlike ceramic or plastic, these are totally shatterproof. It’s lightweight and easy to clean by hand. Please note: Never put the utensil holder in the dishwasher. Made in PRC.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Stainless Steel Utensil Holder As a family-run company that knows and understands the importance of fast, easy, and healthy prepping and storing, we at FineDine hold a very high standard for kitchenware. Our company develops high-quality glassware, serveware, and kitchen tools that not only look great but make the cooking and serving experience all the more pleasurable.

Here’s Why Removable Divider Different strokes for different folks. The utensil caddy is equipped with a sturdy divider, enabling you to organize and classify your utensils. The divider is removable for those who prefer a larger holder that fits more. Attractive Stainless You’re doing it, do it right. Store your utensils in an attractive caddy that’ll bring glory to your kitchen. Eye-catching in its simplistic beauty, durable and sturdy like no other, this utensil holder has a long and glorious future ahead. Space-saving For you in a studio apartment, for you with too few kitchen drawers, for you with more utensils than storage space. Keep all your kitchen utensils organized and collected in a sleek utensil caddy, omitting the need for a drawer.

While you're cooking, at your beck and call. Instantly and immediately access your kitchen utensils with nothing but the flick of a hand. The caddy rotates a full 360°, allowing you to view, insert, and remove from the individual sections. The world is at your fingertips.

reviews.reviewText: Just what I needed and quality better than expected! I am very happy with this purchase and would encourage anyone looking for a counter top utensil canister to purchase this one. I would most certainly purchase this again! Very, very pleased!

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Just what I wanted.
reviews.reviewText: This Rotating Utensil Crock is perfect. It fits all of the tools I use all the time, and I like the sectioning divider for keeping different utensils organized.
